# Environment files — only .env.example is tracked.
# NOTE: .env.development/.staging/.production carry non-secret public web config
# and are intentionally tracked in this sandbox. Real secrets belong in Secret
# Manager / CI, never in these files. .env.local is always ignored.
.env.local
.env.*.local

